subtests.name: keys()/values()/entries() all use the same prototype object
keys() return value is an async iterator of the expected shape
keys(): .next() on empty means forever done, even if you set more
keys(): for-await-of loop body never executes
keys(): error path: returns new rejected promises, each with the same reason
